- She's a girl

610
01:09:10,267 --> 01:09:12,269
It takes time for them
to get ready

611
01:09:18,108 --> 01:09:20,069
"I know I don't
stand a chance, Priya"

612
01:09:20,277 --> 01:09:22,279
"But I don't want to say
If only all my life"

613
01:09:22,696 --> 01:09:26,450
"I tried to make you see reason, Raj...
- I see reason, Priya. I see it"

614
01:09:27,117 --> 01:09:29,286
But my heart won't

615
01:09:32,122 --> 01:09:34,124
"A stranger in an alien land
understands my feelings..."

616
01:09:35,417 --> 01:09:38,087
"but the one who must understand,
won't understand"

617
01:09:38,462 --> 01:09:40,714
"Priya, I have decided.
- What?"

618
01:09:41,131 --> 01:09:43,092
"After our marriage,
I'll cook one meal for us"

619
01:09:43,467 --> 01:09:46,303
I'll look after the kids too

620
01:10:04,154 --> 01:10:07,908
"Remember, there will be someone
happy somewhere in the world..."

621
01:10:08,909 --> 01:10:10,744
because you are happy

622
01:10:41,358 --> 01:10:44,695
"Papa, I have something
to tell you"

623
01:11:24,401 --> 01:11:26,403
"What is happening, grandma?"

624
01:11:28,155 --> 01:11:30,574
Why have you to think so much?

625
01:11:31,200 --> 01:11:33,410
"You're not going to
do as she says, will you?"

626
01:11:35,120 --> 01:11:39,041
Priya's marrying Sameer
and Sameer alone

627
01:11:40,167 --> 01:11:42,795
"Auntie, Priya won't be
happy with the marriage"

628
01:11:43,128 --> 01:11:46,298
And I understand that pretty well.
- But Sameer...

629
01:11:46,632 --> 01:11:52,638
"No, I don't want our marriage
to be based on a compromise"

630
01:11:57,226 --> 01:11:59,603
"Sameer, I came here
for the engagement"

631
01:12:00,437 --> 01:12:04,441
But how was I to know that
all this would happen on the way?

632
01:12:10,280 --> 01:12:13,242
"I understand, Priya.
- You understand nothing, Sameer"

633
01:12:14,159 --> 01:12:17,621
And why are you quiet?
You are the bride's father

634
01:12:18,205 --> 01:12:19,623
Say something

635
01:12:27,256 --> 01:12:32,469
"My child, are you sure he's a nice
boy and that he'll keep you happy?"

636
01:12:34,346 --> 01:12:36,473
Yes.
- Why don't you meet him?

637
01:12:37,015 --> 01:12:40,310
What's gotten into all of you?
You even want to meet him now?

638
01:12:41,353 --> 01:12:44,147
What's wrong in meeting him?
- He must be in the plane by now.

639
01:12:44,481 --> 01:12:46,483
He left four hours ago

640
01:12:47,442 --> 01:12:50,112
"No, aunt. He mustn't have gone away"

641
01:12:51,321 --> 01:12:56,285
"Papa, if I know him well,
he must still be waiting for me"

642
01:13:01,540 --> 01:13:05,711
May I and stop Raj? Please?

643
01:15:11,878 --> 01:15:13,964
"Yours must be the first step
in our house, Priya"

644
01:15:17,425 --> 01:15:19,177
What happened?
- One second

645
01:15:19,553 --> 01:15:21,221
I'll go in for a while

646
01:15:22,305 --> 01:15:24,224
Something important to do...
I'll be back soon

647
01:15:24,516 --> 01:15:27,477
"Don't worry. I'll take you in.
I've married you, after all"

648
01:15:27,811 --> 01:15:29,146
One minute

649
01:15:43,410 --> 01:15:46,663
"I'm coming in, Raj.
- Wait..."

650
01:15:51,501 --> 01:15:53,920
Let no one say that we didn't
complete the rituals

651
01:15:54,671 --> 01:15:57,674
"It's actually meant to be done
by my mother, but right now..."

652
01:16:12,439 --> 01:16:13,690
Red ink

653
01:16:14,399 --> 01:16:16,234
Let me do it

654
01:16:26,536 --> 01:16:28,496
This is also meant to be done
by someone elderly...

655
01:16:28,705 --> 01:16:31,041
"but since I'm doing everything,
this one too..."

656
01:16:33,877 --> 01:16:39,799
Now for this ritual.
I don't know who performs it...

657
01:16:40,467 --> 01:16:42,844
but it's performed all right.
I know that

658
01:16:47,724 --> 01:16:49,559
May I come over?
- Please

659
01:16:49,893 --> 01:16:52,395
But mind your step.
Don't slip on the talcum powder

660
01:17:21,633 --> 01:17:24,886
"Priya, this is our house"

661
01:17:41,611 --> 01:17:42,779
It's nice

662
01:17:49,702 --> 01:17:51,371
"You're already up, Raj?"

663
01:17:52,539 --> 01:17:54,416
I didn't go to sleep all night

664
01:17:54,749 --> 01:17:57,460
And I never got better sleep
than this

665
01:17:59,587 --> 01:18:03,800
"What are you wearing, Raj?
- This is Allah Mian"

666
01:18:04,551 --> 01:18:06,219
Allah Mian?
- God

667
01:18:06,553 --> 01:18:08,972
You know Salim?
His mother gave it to me

668
01:18:09,556 --> 01:18:15,937
"Know what? Whatever I ask Him for,
He gives it to me"

669
01:18:16,938 --> 01:18:18,940
Like you. I have you

670
01:18:20,567 --> 01:18:24,821
"You always carry Him with you?
- Yes, He's always with me"

671
01:18:27,615 --> 01:18:30,618
I feel incomplete without Him

672
01:18:32,579 --> 01:18:34,372
Won't you even give Him to me?

673
01:18:37,834 --> 01:18:39,169
One moment

674
01:18:43,840 --> 01:18:48,178
"God, if something
ever happens to me..."

675
01:18:49,679 --> 01:18:51,347
if I'm no more...

676
01:18:52,849 --> 01:18:54,851
do look after my Priya

677
01:18:55,810 --> 01:18:58,188
Because even she doesn't know
how much I love her

678
01:18:59,856 --> 01:19:04,861
I love Priya very very much

679
01:19:11,951 --> 01:19:15,163
We'll always remain together Raj

680
01:19:31,721 --> 01:19:35,099
I didn't find a love story
like this even in fairytales

681
01:19:38,978 --> 01:19:41,898
"Sorry guys, I'm late.
I'm sick of this traffic"

682
01:19:42,899 --> 01:19:45,902
"I told you, you're never on time.
And they..."

683
01:19:51,741 --> 01:19:54,452
"Salim, this is my fiancee Sheetal"

684
01:19:55,745 --> 01:19:58,706
"This is Salim and that
is his wife, Farah"

685
01:19:59,415 --> 01:20:02,585
We got stuck in the traffic...
- I told him

686
01:20:02,919 --> 01:20:06,589
"No, it isn't about that. Actually,
while waiting for you..."

687
01:20:06,923 --> 01:20:09,592
I heard a wonderful love story.
- Which one?

688
01:20:09,926 --> 01:20:11,928
Raj and Priya's love-story

689
01:20:16,933 --> 01:20:19,602
I'd like to meet
Raj and Priya some day

690
01:20:19,936 --> 01:20:21,479
Oh certainly

691
01:20:21,813 --> 01:20:24,816
"You're very lucky, Sheetal.
- How come?"

692
01:20:25,191 --> 01:20:29,737
Because today is the first wedding
anniversary of Raj and Priya!

693
01:20:35,702 --> 01:20:37,954
It's their surprise party
we're going to today

694
01:20:40,373 --> 01:20:43,376
Sonofagun! Couldn't you tell me
that over the phone?

695
01:20:43,710 --> 01:20:46,379
"If I told you, the surprise
wouldn't be a surprise anymore"

696
01:20:46,713 --> 01:20:49,173
"Let's go, we're getting late.
- But where is the party?"

697
01:20:49,507 --> 01:20:52,468
On the terrace of their building.
C'mon

698
01:20:54,971 --> 01:20:56,264
"Come, come..."

699
01:20:57,765 --> 01:21:02,353
"Manubhai, why have you brought us here?
- Don't ask, just see what I've done"

700
01:21:02,687 --> 01:21:05,314
Now look...
- What will I look at in the darkness?

701
01:21:06,691 --> 01:21:08,317
What's here anyway?

702
01:21:17,994 --> 01:21:19,996
"I'm Sheetal, Deepak's fiance!"

703
01:21:22,123 --> 01:21:25,376
"When they told me about your
love story, I couldn't believe..."

704
01:21:25,710 --> 01:21:28,337
that someone could have a romance
like yours in our times!

705
01:21:36,012 --> 01:21:38,806
"Manubhai, this surprise party
is great fun!"

706
01:21:48,024 --> 01:21:49,817
"Quiet, quiet!"

707
01:21:50,651 --> 01:21:52,695
"For two hours, this is what
we were talking about..."

708
01:21:53,029 --> 01:21:56,741
"and you want to fight even here!
- Not me, Raj. You want to fight"

709
01:21:57,033 --> 01:22:00,453
Priya! You've changed so much
in the past one year

710
01:22:00,870 --> 01:22:03,497
You are the one who has changed?
- Have I?

711
01:22:03,873 --> 01:22:06,042
You're fighting with me
on our first wedding anniversary...

712
01:22:06,375 --> 01:22:08,711
and you say I've changed?
- Do you think I like fighting...

713
01:22:09,045 --> 01:22:13,216
with you on our first anniversary?
But you're not the man I got married to!

714
01:22:15,843 --> 01:22:17,762
You married the wrong man!

715
01:22:18,054 --> 01:22:20,056
Just leave me then!

716
01:22:29,815 --> 01:22:31,817
At least sweeten
each other's tongue first

717
01:22:37,823 --> 01:22:39,867
Your turn. Come on!

718
01:23:07,645 --> 01:23:09,897
Looks like the lady isn't
in a nice mood this morning

719
01:23:10,439 --> 01:23:13,025
You were even late in coming.
Is everything all right?

720
01:23:13,442 --> 01:23:16,153
I didn't sleep well last night.
- No? That's nice

721
01:23:16,487 --> 01:23:18,614
Were you thinking about me?
- No

722
01:23:19,657 --> 01:23:22,076
I was thinking what a huge
nuisance marriage is

723
01:23:22,451 --> 01:23:24,412
What does it mean?
- Problem if you marry...

724
01:23:24,620 --> 01:23:27,081
problem if you don't.
- What makes you say that?

725
01:23:27,415 --> 01:23:30,292
Look at Raj and Priya. It was
supposed to be a great love affair

726
01:23:30,626 --> 01:23:32,753
"But what happened?
- Yes, what happened?"

727
01:23:33,462 --> 01:23:36,257
Hold on... are you talking
about last night?

728
01:23:38,634 --> 01:23:41,095
Every man and wife have
their share of problems

729
01:23:41,470 --> 01:23:43,431
That doesn't mean they aren't
happy with each other

730
01:23:43,681 --> 01:23:46,434
I know Raj.
He loves Priya very much

731
01:23:46,809 --> 01:23:49,478
Loving your wife doesn't
make you a very nice husband

732
01:23:49,812 --> 01:23:53,441
"Really? The way you talk, it seems as
if you've done a Phd on marriages"

733
01:23:53,816 --> 01:23:55,109
What?
- You haven't said this...

734
01:23:55,317 --> 01:23:57,111
"to anyone else, have you?
- No"

735
01:23:57,445 --> 01:24:01,073
And please don't!
People will laugh at you

736
01:24:01,449 --> 01:24:04,076
Raj and Priya love
each other very much

737
01:24:20,301 --> 01:24:24,013
Raj is always late. He knows
Priya doesn't like it at all

738
01:24:34,315 --> 01:24:37,359
Your son-in-law hasn't arrived yet?
- What can I do?

739
01:24:37,693 --> 01:24:41,363
I asked him before holding a ritual
for their peaceful future

740
01:24:41,697 --> 01:24:45,826
But the boys nowadays...!
- Praise the Lord!

741
01:24:49,497 --> 01:24:51,332
His phone's not working

742
01:24:55,503 --> 01:24:58,005
See your friend?
He's still missing

743
01:24:58,464 --> 01:25:01,967
"He's late, but I'm sure
he'll come"

744
01:25:06,722 --> 01:25:11,518
"My child, the ritual is over
and your husband hasn't arrived?"

745
01:25:11,894 --> 01:25:15,189
He has already left the office.
He should be here any moment

746
01:25:15,522 --> 01:25:18,525
It was necessary for both of you
to be present at this ritual

747
01:25:19,735 --> 01:25:21,904
The auspicious hour has
passed already

748
01:25:22,529 --> 01:25:25,032
We can't wait anymore

749
01:25:29,745 --> 01:25:32,331
All right. You may do
as you think fit

750
01:25:33,540 --> 01:25:39,505
We will now pray to God
to bless you both

751
01:25:50,683 --> 01:25:55,145
This spinach looks delicious.
And the chickpeas smell great

752
01:25:55,479 --> 01:25:58,232
Nobody makes chickpea
like you do... enough

753
01:25:59,692 --> 01:26:01,443
Sit... down

754
01:26:03,779 --> 01:26:07,992
"How will this do, Priya?
I've said sorry, sought forgiveness"

755
01:26:08,492 --> 01:26:10,577
It's all over...
at least talk to me now

756
01:26:10,828 --> 01:26:13,789
How will it do if you don't talk?

757
01:26:16,834 --> 01:26:21,088
"All right. If you're not eating
with me, I'm not eating too"

758
01:26:25,801 --> 01:26:30,264
"Priya, talk to me! I told you,
I made a mistake. I'm sorry!"

759
01:26:30,597 --> 01:26:33,809
"You say sorry, but how about the
ritual aunt Anna held for us?"

760
01:26:34,143 --> 01:26:36,145
Do you realise how
insulted I felt?

761
01:26:38,814 --> 01:26:42,609
I was coming any way.
But Mr Malhotra showed up

762
01:26:42,943 --> 01:26:45,487
And you know how important
Mr Malhotra is for our business

763
01:26:45,821 --> 01:26:47,823
I know how important
your business is!

764
01:26:48,157 --> 01:26:50,909
Where was your business when you
followed me all the way to Greece?

765
01:26:51,660 --> 01:26:54,913
It had to do with love then.
- With love?

766
01:26:55,247 --> 01:26:57,541
So where is your love now?
- But we're already married

767
01:26:57,833 --> 01:27:00,043
"What does that mean, Raj?"

768
01:27:01,837 --> 01:27:05,132
Just that one marries
the one he loves

769
01:27:05,466 --> 01:27:07,426
"And love is always there,
or why would the marriage be?"

770
01:27:07,634 --> 01:27:10,262
"I mean, love goes in a bit of a
background after marriage..."

771
01:27:10,596 --> 01:27:13,849
"You're in love, I'm in love...
we're loved ones"

772
01:27:15,851 --> 01:27:17,853
Shit! What am I saying!

773
01:27:19,563 --> 01:27:22,524
"Priya, listen to me.
That wasn't what I meant to say"

774
01:27:22,858 --> 01:27:24,526
I was confused

775
01:27:24,860 --> 01:27:27,696
"What I meant to say is that after
marriage, one becomes responsible"

776
01:27:28,030 --> 01:27:31,366
So you say you're responsible?
- Hundred per cent responsible!

777
01:27:31,700 --> 01:27:33,619
"You're hundred per cent
responsible, right?"

778
01:27:33,869 --> 01:27:37,664
"This is your shirt, isn't it? But you
took it off and kept it on the sofa"

779
01:27:38,040 --> 01:27:40,584
"If you wished, you could also keep
it with the laundry, couldn't you?"

780
01:27:40,876 --> 01:27:43,212
But you won't.
And your shoes always...

781
01:27:44,046 --> 01:27:45,214
Which shoes?

782
01:27:48,675 --> 01:27:50,677
"What?
- You just picked them up, didn't you?"

783
01:27:51,762 --> 01:27:55,307
"You just picked them up, didn't you?
- All right, but I picked them up"

784
01:27:55,641 --> 01:27:58,018
Why wouldn't you do it earlier?

785
01:28:01,605 --> 01:28:05,234
"All right, I won't smile! But let's
decide what you're complaining about!"

786
01:28:05,567 --> 01:28:08,570
"That I'm late, I didn't get to the
temple, my shoes, my smile...?"

787
01:28:08,904 --> 01:28:11,698
What is it that you complain about?
- I complain about everything you do!

788
01:28:12,032 --> 01:28:14,576
"Everything?
- There's a way of living together, Raj"

789
01:28:14,910 --> 01:28:17,329
Now hold on! You're going to
teach me to live together?

790
01:28:17,663 --> 01:28:19,581
The large-hearted one...

791
01:28:19,957 --> 01:28:25,003
Shut up! What silly song is that!
We're have a fight going here!

792
01:28:31,718 --> 01:28:34,596
I'm no kid for you to...

793
01:28:34,930 --> 01:28:35,931
Shut up!

794
01:28:37,099 --> 01:28:39,601
"So stop lecturing me, please"

795
01:28:39,935 --> 01:28:42,271
"It's not wrong to point
someone's mistakes, Raj"

796
01:28:43,897 --> 01:28:44,940
Mistakes...?

797
01:28:48,944 --> 01:28:52,114
"You say mistakes, Priya. But it's
not always my mistake"

798
01:28:52,447 --> 01:28:55,200
You make mistakes several times
and I still say sorry

799
01:28:55,534 --> 01:28:59,746
So you're saying you're perfect?
- Did I say that...?

800
01:29:01,832 --> 01:29:05,627
"I'm not perfect, Priya. You...
you think Nandu's perfect?"

801
01:29:05,961 --> 01:29:08,964
He's not.
None of us is perfect

802
01:29:11,758 --> 01:29:14,344
I come back home after
a hard day's work...

803
01:29:14,678 --> 01:29:17,097
I feel like sitting down
and chatting with you...

804
01:29:17,764 --> 01:29:21,977
or the two of us having
a cup of coffee in the balcony

805
01:29:26,898 --> 01:29:29,985
You want romance?
And chat with me?

806
01:29:30,736 --> 01:29:32,404
With the tv on?

807
01:29:34,990 --> 01:29:38,410
"I switched on the tv because...
- That's your daily routine, Raj"

808
01:29:38,744 --> 01:29:41,455
You come home every day
and sit down before the tv

809
01:29:41,788 --> 01:29:44,458
I too want you to talk to me
when you come back home

810
01:29:44,791 --> 01:29:46,460
But you'll never understand...

811
01:29:48,003 --> 01:29:51,840
I've switched off the tv.
So let's talk. Please. Come on

812
01:29:52,174 --> 01:29:55,135
What did you do in the office today?
- Let's not talk about the office

813
01:29:55,719 --> 01:29:58,346
Because I'm sick of office-talk
while I'm in the office

814
01:29:58,805 --> 01:30:01,475
"When I come back home, I feel like
talking about something else"

815
01:30:01,808 --> 01:30:04,436
But you talk of nothing else Raj.
You begin to watch tv!

816
01:30:04,811 --> 01:30:07,230
"But I only catch up with the news!
- News, Cricket match and...!"

817
01:30:08,023 --> 01:30:11,485
"You're right and I'm wrong, okay?
- No, you're not wrong"

818
01:30:11,818 --> 01:30:16,698
"I'm wrong! And I'm sorry!
- Please, Raj! Stop saying sorry"

819
01:30:17,032 --> 01:30:19,701
And I'm not going to forget
today's insult ever

820
01:30:20,035 --> 01:30:23,038
What insult?
And I can't even say sorry!

821
01:30:23,789 --> 01:30:25,791
I want to sleep.
- So sleep

822
01:30:26,041 --> 01:30:28,043
Have your food and switch
off the lights

823
01:30:28,168 --> 01:30:30,712
Why must I eat? You took away
my plate! And the lights...?

824
01:30:31,046 --> 01:30:33,715
Why must you have everything your way?
The lights are not being switched off!

825
01:30:34,049 --> 01:30:37,052
Let me see who switches them off!
- All right. Let the lights remain

826
01:30:52,067 --> 01:30:54,653
"Milkman, can't you come
a bit early?"

827
01:30:55,070 --> 01:30:58,490
My husband's been pestering
me for tea all morning!

828
01:30:58,824 --> 01:31:01,535
"But I can come only when the
Buffalo starts milking, right?"

829
01:31:01,868 --> 01:31:04,746
You have a new excuse every day.
If you don't come on time tomorrow...

830
01:31:05,080 --> 01:31:08,750
I'll stop your supply and
take milk from the dairy instead

831
01:31:09,084 --> 01:31:10,919
You get that?
- All right

832
01:31:14,798 --> 01:31:16,633
Milk for 2 rupees

833
01:31:18,093 --> 01:31:21,680
"Nandu, have you given up booze
and started drinking milk instead?"

834
01:31:22,013 --> 01:31:26,768
Not for me. It's for Moti.
Can't you see how skinny he's become?

835
01:31:27,102 --> 01:31:28,436
Smell him

836
01:31:29,771 --> 01:31:34,234
He's in bad shape.
He needs calcium

837
01:31:42,284 --> 01:31:44,077
"Your juice, Raj"

838
01:31:44,119 --> 01:31:46,454
Breakfast is lying on the table.
Have it before you leave

839
01:31:47,122 --> 01:31:49,416
There's no saying when
you'll have lunch anyway

840
01:31:51,042 --> 01:31:53,628
"I just scrubbed the floor, Raj.
What are you doing?"

841
01:31:54,087 --> 01:31:56,798
What?
- You've wet the pillow

842
01:31:57,132 --> 01:31:59,676
It's my pillow.
I use it

843
01:32:00,010 --> 01:32:01,636
And... all right

844
01:32:05,724 --> 01:32:07,309
Is it okay now?

845
01:32:10,937 --> 01:32:13,440
"What's that now?
- You'll wet the bedsheet, Raj"

846
01:32:14,107 --> 01:32:17,152
What arguments do we get
caught up in every morning?

847
01:32:17,444 --> 01:32:19,821
"I haven't started the argument, Raj.
- The way you..."

848
01:32:20,155 --> 01:32:22,282
how will I do any work at
the office in this mood?

849
01:32:22,657 --> 01:32:24,659
Your mood gets spoilt
every now and then

850
01:32:25,160 --> 01:32:27,954
"But naturally, Priya!
It's because of what you say!"

851
01:32:28,288 --> 01:32:31,333
You tell me how to go about
every little thing

852
01:32:31,666 --> 01:32:34,836
"This isn't right. Don't keep
the shoe here, someone might trip"

853
01:32:35,170 --> 01:32:39,424
Must I keep the shoes on my head?
How's anyone going to trip on shoes?

854
01:32:39,883 --> 01:32:41,968
Do you fall over this ironing board
which is lying here?

855
01:32:42,302 --> 01:32:44,596
Do you fall over the bed?
But you'll trip over the shoes

856
01:32:44,929 --> 01:32:47,849
"You're always picking on my shoes!
- What wrong have I said, Raj?"

857
01:32:48,183 --> 01:32:50,185
"I just want some cleanliness
to be maintained, isn't it?"

858
01:32:50,518 --> 01:32:53,521
"What's wrong if our house is clean?
- It's wrong, very wrong!"

859
01:32:54,189 --> 01:32:56,274
I like to have my room littered

860
01:32:56,900 --> 01:32:59,861
"I want one of my shoes to lie here,
and one to lie there"

861
01:33:00,195 --> 01:33:01,988
I want to see who
trips over them!

862
01:33:02,197 --> 01:33:05,325
It's because I'm illiterate!
I'm a bloody bum!

863
01:33:05,742 --> 01:33:09,329
"I like to have my pillow
at my feet, not my head"

864
01:33:09,704 --> 01:33:12,540
And these blankets mustn't be
on the bed when I'm about to sleep

865
01:33:12,916 --> 01:33:16,002
"And this towel, wherever I take it off
is the right place"

866
01:33:17,170 --> 01:33:20,673
"I agree, I don't know how to live.
I don't know it at all"

867
01:33:21,007 --> 01:33:23,551
Only you know it!
And what can I do?

868
01:33:23,927 --> 01:33:25,929
I got married for the first time!

869
01:33:28,014 --> 01:33:29,974
"It's my first marriage too, Raj"

870
01:33:31,101 --> 01:33:33,353
And throw away that bedsheet too

871
01:34:25,071 --> 01:34:26,739
"What are you doing, Priya?"

872
01:34:29,200 --> 01:34:30,785
People are watching!

873
01:35:14,287 --> 01:35:17,915
"Goodness!
The signs you make..."

874
01:35:19,334 --> 01:35:23,004
they make me crazy about you

875
01:35:24,881 --> 01:35:29,344
What secrets are you exposing...

876
01:35:30,094 --> 01:35:34,557
"what are you telling me
with your eyes?"

877
01:35:35,099 --> 01:35:38,353
You do wield all the magic

878
01:35:39,479 --> 01:35:43,358
"Goodness!
The signs you make..."

879
01:35:44,609 --> 01:35:48,529
they make me crazy about you

880
01:35:50,156 --> 01:35:54,911
"You are the one who
touches my heartstrings"

881
01:35:55,370 --> 01:35:59,832
Why would anyone meeting you...

882
01:36:00,208 --> 01:36:03,669
not lose her heart to you

883
01:36:30,696 --> 01:36:35,034
"Your lush body,
casts a spell"

884
01:36:35,493 --> 01:36:39,997
"Your dense tresses
exude a fragrance"

885
01:36:40,498 --> 01:36:45,128
"On my breath
lingers a scent..."

886
01:36:45,628 --> 01:36:49,841
"because your eyes
are going astray"

887
01:36:50,216 --> 01:36:55,096
"Your body is as beautiful
as the rosegardens..."

888
01:36:55,763 --> 01:36:59,058
"the sight of it
drives me out of my senses"

889
01:37:00,309 --> 01:37:04,438
"Goodness!
The signs you make..."

890
01:37:34,010 --> 01:37:38,264
"An intoxication
is taking over..."

891
01:37:38,723 --> 01:37:43,060
I'm barely in my senses

892
01:37:43,477 --> 01:37:47,982
I'm lost to myself too...

893
01:37:48,482 --> 01:37:52,820
"I awake
but I feel as if I'm asleep"

894
01:37:53,154 --> 01:37:58,117
"Keep swaying,
keep melting..."

895
01:37:58,576 --> 01:38:02,038
when you are in my arms

896
01:38:03,331 --> 01:38:07,293
"Goodness!
The signs you make..."

897
01:38:08,294 --> 01:38:12,298
they make me crazy about you

